Scrape FanGraphs.com Guts!

Source: R/fg_guts.R
fg_guts.Rd

Scrape historical FanGraphs Guts! table, wOBA, FIP coefficients and constants

Usage

fg_guts()

Value

Returns a tibble of seasonal constants from FanGraphs

col_nametypes
seasoninteger
lg_wobanumeric
woba_scalenumeric
wBBnumeric
wHBPnumeric
w1Bnumeric
w2Bnumeric
w3Bnumeric
wHRnumeric
runSBnumeric
runCSnumeric
lg_r_panumeric
lg_r_wnumeric
cFIPnumeric
